Office of Disciplinary Counsel v. Rothermel.

[Cite as Disciplinary Counsel v. Rothermel (1999), 86 Ohio St.3d 1215.]

(No. DD 84-20 Submitted and decided September 9, 1999.)

For earlier case, see Disciplinary Counsel v. Rothermel (1984), 15 Ohio St.3d 121, 15 OBR 272, 472 N.E.2d 1072.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
